description: This mellow yellow truck is moseying through Kansas City and absolutely delighting all the local foodies with their marvelous made-from-scratch Mediterranean cuisine. This super friendly crew is serving delicious pita dishes in which you can load up with delectable Lamb, Chicken, or Veggies. You’ll also find a variety of sides, all delightfully bursting with Mediterranean flavor. So if you’re looking for some pretty great tasting grub, come eat at Pita for Good.
name: Pita For Good
